Require agentgrep

Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-ui-filter.gif
Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-ui-filter.mp4
Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-ui-filter.webm

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1900
Set Height 700
Source docs/_static/demos/vhs/_preamble.tape

Sleep 1s
Type "agentgrep ui"
Enter
Sleep 4s
Type "cache OR retry"
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 3500ms
Down
Sleep 300ms
Type "codex"
Sleep 1800ms
Ctrl+U
Sleep 300ms
Type "gemini"
Sleep 1800ms
Ctrl+U
Sleep 1200ms
Ctrl+C
Sleep 350ms
Ctrl+C
Wait
Sleep 1500ms
